I will do everything for her
to get surgery.

213
00:13:21,733 --> 00:13:24,200
I can't bear it!

214
00:13:24,333 --> 00:13:27,000
I can't bear to lose my child!

215
00:13:44,267 --> 00:13:45,333
You look stressed.

216
00:13:47,033 --> 00:13:49,133
Why?

217
