267
00:16:19,300 --> 00:16:21,367
I won't be able to come home.

268
00:16:21,500 --> 00:16:25,600
I need to work
to pay off my debt.

269
00:16:25,733 --> 00:16:28,567
And the plane ticket also costs
a lot of money.

270
00:16:28,700 --> 00:16:30,533
Instead of paying
for the ticket,

271
00:16:30,667 --> 00:16:33,133
I'll just send you the money.

272
00:16:33,267 --> 00:16:35,300
We understand.

273
00:16:35,433 --> 00:16:36,567
Love.

274
00:16:36,700 --> 00:16:38,567
Thank you so much...

275
00:16:38,700 --> 00:16:42,600
for all your sacrifices
for our family.

276
00:16:42,767 --> 00:16:44,700
It's okay, but...

277
00:16:44,833 --> 00:16:48,033
I'm not perfect, Love. So...

278
00:16:48,167 --> 00:16:50,200
despite the shortcomings
I may have...

279
00:16:50,333 --> 00:16:52,467
please be understanding.

280
00:16:54,633 --> 00:16:55,767
What do you mean?

281
00:16:57,433 --> 00:16:58,567
Are you okay?

282
00:16:59,600 --> 00:17:01,267
It's nothing, just remember...

283
00:17:03,267 --> 00:17:07,667
everything I do is for you
and for our children.

284
00:17:09,333 --> 00:17:11,667
All the sacrifices I make...

285
00:17:13,267 --> 00:17:15,233
it's because I love you all
so much.

286
00:17:15,400 --> 00:17:16,467
Manuel...

287
00:17:16,600 --> 00:17:18,733
we love you so much too.

288
00:17:20,133 --> 00:17:21,967
Okay, Love.

289
00:17:22,100 --> 00:17:24,200
Please know that
I love you so much.

290
00:17:46,200 --> 00:17:49,933
Under the laws of the
Republic of the Philippines,

291
00:17:50,100 --> 00:17:52,867
I ask you, Hazel Capistrano,

292
00:17:53,000 --> 00:17:56,333
if you freely and voluntarily
consent

293
00:17:56,467 --> 00:17:59,867
to be united in marriage
to Manuel Cruz?

294
00:18:07,233 --> 00:18:08,267
I do.

295
00:18:40,233 --> 00:18:43,533
Under the laws of the
Republic of the Philippines,

296
00:18:43,667 --> 00:18:46,567
I ask you, Manuel Cruz,

297
00:18:46,700 --> 00:18:49,600
if you freely
and voluntarily consent

298
00:18:49,733 --> 00:18:51,900
to be united in marriage

299
00:18:52,033 --> 00:18:53,767
to Hazel Capistrano?

300
00:19:00,067 --> 00:19:02,267
<i>I wonder if we're
in this situation</i>

301
00:19:03,700 --> 00:19:06,000
<i> because God is punishing us.</i>

302
00:19:08,233 --> 00:19:09,233
<i> Because until now,</i>

303
00:19:09,367 --> 00:19:10,933
<i>our relationship remains
without God's blessing.</i>

304
00:19:12,267 --> 00:19:13,433
<i> Love...</i>

305
00:19:15,133 --> 00:19:18,733
<i>Are we really going to talk
about marriage right now?</i>

306
00:19:18,867 --> 00:19:20,500
<i> We'll discuss that later,</i>

307
00:19:20,633 --> 00:19:22,867
<i>we have to prioritize Andrea
for now.</i>

308
00:19:30,167 --> 00:19:31,700
Mom...

309
00:19:31,833 --> 00:19:37,667
Are they going to cut
my lungs and heart?

310
00:19:42,033 --> 00:19:43,533
Sweetie, they will put you to
sleep.

311
00:19:43,667 --> 00:19:46,267
You won't feel any pain.

312
00:19:46,400 --> 00:19:49,833
Just remember
after the surgery...

313
00:19:49,967 --> 00:19:51,700
you will get better.

314
00:19:51,833 --> 00:19:54,333
We will be happy again.

315
00:20:09,800 --> 00:20:12,967
I'm scared.

316
00:20:14,333 --> 00:20:17,433
I want Dad to hug me.

317
00:20:18,467 --> 00:20:21,667
Because when he hugs me...

318
00:20:23,333 --> 00:20:26,533
I don't feel scared anymore.

319
00:20:44,267 --> 00:20:46,300
Will Mommy's hug
be enough for now?

320
00:20:47,467 --> 00:20:49,233
I love you, Mom.

321
00:20:50,867 --> 00:20:52,333
I love you too, Andrea.

322
00:20:53,567 --> 00:20:55,333
Don't be scared,

323
00:20:55,467 --> 00:20:57,833
I'll be right outside.

324
00:20:57,967 --> 00:21:00,400
I'll be right outside
waiting for you.

325
00:21:35,267 --> 00:21:36,967
Please, God.

326
00:21:53,300 --> 00:21:54,367
I do.

327
00:22:00,767 --> 00:22:02,267
By the power vested in me,

328
00:22:02,400 --> 00:22:04,900
I pronounce you
husband and wife.

329
00:22:46,400 --> 00:22:48,767
I'm glad
we have a nice landlady.

330
00:22:49,867 --> 00:22:52,100
She agreed to reserve this
apartment for us

331
00:22:52,233 --> 00:22:55,533
until my employer releases
my housing allowance.

332
00:22:58,567 --> 00:22:59,533
It's nice, right?

333
00:23:00,600 --> 00:23:01,800
I'm going to take a shower,
okay?

334
00:23:01,933 --> 00:23:03,400
Can you take care of our stuff?

335
00:23:03,533 --> 00:23:05,033
Just take care of the
stuff you can carry,

336
00:23:05,167 --> 00:23:06,933
then we'll take care
of the others tomorrow.

337
00:23:07,067 --> 00:23:08,600
Okay?

338
00:23:08,733 --> 00:23:10,567
I'll take this one.

339
00:23:44,600 --> 00:23:45,900
Hello, Love?

340
00:23:46,033 --> 00:23:48,633
How is Andrea's surgery?

341
00:23:48,767 --> 00:23:49,833
It's done now.

342
00:23:50,933 --> 00:23:55,100
They've successfully
closed the hole in her heart.

343
00:23:55,267 --> 00:23:56,867
Thank God.

344
00:23:58,400 --> 00:24:02,400
But they still need to observe
her for the next few hours.

345
00:24:02,533 --> 00:24:05,600
It's possible
to have complications.

346
00:24:05,733 --> 00:24:09,600
She might get rapid heartbeats.

347
00:24:09,733 --> 00:24:12,867
She might get an infection.

348
00:24:13,000 --> 00:24:14,300
That's not going to happen.

349
00:24:14,433 --> 00:24:16,100
She will get better now.
I'm sure of it.

350
00:24:17,000 --> 00:24:18,500
Thank you.

351
00:24:18,633 --> 00:24:21,167
If not for your hard work,

352
00:24:21,300 --> 00:24:23,733
she wouldn't get surgery.

353
00:24:23,867 --> 00:24:25,133
Manuel?

354
00:24:27,233 --> 00:24:28,800
Manuel?

355
00:24:28,967 --> 00:24:30,367
Manuel?

356
00:24:30,500 --> 00:24:32,267
- Who's that?
- Manuel?

357
00:24:32,400 --> 00:24:35,367
- Oh, that?
- Have you seen my toiletries?

358
00:24:35,500 --> 00:24:36,900
That's a woman's voice.

359
00:24:37,933 --> 00:24:39,433
Are you with a woman right now?

360
00:24:39,567 --> 00:24:41,667
She's my co-worker's cousin.

361
00:24:41,800 --> 00:24:43,667
I have to go.
I'll call you again, okay?

362
00:24:43,800 --> 00:24:45,900
Okay, be safe, Love.

363
00:24:46,033 --> 00:24:47,267
You, too.

364
00:24:47,400 --> 00:24:48,733
Hello?

365
00:24:48,867 --> 00:24:49,833
Hello?

366
00:24:58,567 --> 00:24:59,533
Love?

367
00:25:02,633 --> 00:25:04,800
You still call her Love?

368
00:25:05,867 --> 00:25:07,733
Isn't she your ex now?

369
00:25:07,867 --> 00:25:09,700
I just want to remind you

370
00:25:09,833 --> 00:25:11,867
that I'm your wife now.

371
00:25:16,667 --> 00:25:17,567
<i> What are you going to do now?</i>

372
00:25:17,700 --> 00:25:19,567
<i>You'll cut contact
with your family?</i>

373
00:25:19,700 --> 00:25:20,667
<i> I can't do that.</i>

374
00:25:20,800 --> 00:25:22,900
<i>How am I going to know
how they're doing?</i>

375
00:25:24,800 --> 00:25:28,000
I was just thinking,
what if Felma finds out?

376
00:25:28,133 --> 00:25:30,267
You're being too strict
with him.

377
00:25:30,400 --> 00:25:31,533
Why not?

378
00:25:31,667 --> 00:25:33,567
He's mine now.

379
00:25:33,700 --> 00:25:35,700
I have every right
to protect what's mine.

380
00:25:35,867 --> 00:25:37,633
Who's the girl
you're with in the picture?

381
00:25:37,767 --> 00:25:38,967
What picture?

382
00:25:39,100 --> 00:25:41,367
Your picture at your
friend's birthday party.

383
00:25:41,500 --> 00:25:43,367
Abel is also in the picture.

384
00:25:43,500 --> 00:25:44,900
The girl is holding on to you.

385
00:25:45,033 --> 00:25:46,033
Is that Hazel?

386
00:25:46,167 --> 00:25:49,267
- Hello, Love?
- Stop calling him, Love.

387
00:25:49,400 --> 00:25:50,767
Are you Hazel?

388
00:25:50,900 --> 00:25:52,100
Oh, yes.

389
00:25:52,233 --> 00:25:54,233
Hazel Capistrano.

390
00:25:54,367 --> 00:25:55,433
And may I add...

391
00:25:55,567 --> 00:25:56,700
Cruz.

392
00:25:56,833 --> 00:25:59,267
Because I'm now
Mrs. Manuel Cruz.

393
00:25:59,400 --> 00:26:00,833
Manuel and I are married.

394
00:26:00,967 --> 00:26:01,767
Oh, here he is.

395
00:26:01,900 --> 00:26:03,233
Talk to Manuel.

396
00:26:03,367 --> 00:26:04,667
You called Felma?

397
00:26:04,800 --> 00:26:07,433
Manuel, is that woman
telling the truth?

398
00:26:07,567 --> 00:26:09,533
Is she your wife now?

399
00:26:09,700 --> 00:26:11,867
Felma, wait. Let me explain.

400
00:26:12,000 --> 00:26:13,800
Answer me!

401
00:26:13,933 --> 00:26:15,233
Is it true?

402
00:26:15,367 --> 00:26:17,333
You don't understand.

403
00:26:17,467 --> 00:26:19,133
Is it true?
